<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q19_v4" title="Q19_v4" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>
      Ana resuelve la expresión
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:msup>
            <m:mn>6</m:mn>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn>
          </m:msup>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo>
          <m:msup>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            <m:mn>4</m:mn>
          </m:msup>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
      de la siguiente manera:<br/>
      (1)
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:msup>
            <m:mn>6</m:mn>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn>
          </m:msup>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo>
          <m:msup>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            <m:mn>4</m:mn>
          </m:msup>
          <m:mo>=</m:mo>
          <m:msup>
            <m:mn>6</m:mn>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn>
          </m:msup>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo>
          <m:mn>16</m:mn>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
      <br/>
      (2)
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:msup>
            <m:mn>6</m:mn>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn>
          </m:msup>
          <m:mo>=</m:mo>
          <m:mn>1</m:mn>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
      <br/>
      (3) Entonces,
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:msup>
            <m:mn>6</m:mn>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn>
          </m:msup>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo>
          <m:msup>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            <m:mn>4</m:mn>
          </m:msup>
          <m:mo>=</m:mo>
          <m:mn>1</m:mn>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo>
          <m:mn>16</m:mn>
          <m:mo>=</m:mo>
          <m:mn>17</m:mn>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
      .<br/><br/>
      ¿Qué explicación justifica correctamente el paso (2)?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        Porque
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:msup>
              <m:mn>6</m:mn>
              <m:mn>0</m:mn>
            </m:msup>
            <m:mo>=</m:mo>
            <m:mn>6</m:mn>
            <m:mo>·</m:mo>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        , y todo número multiplicado por
        <m:math>
          <m:mn>0</m:mn>
        </m:math>
        da
        <m:math>
          <m:mn>0</m:mn>
        </m:math>
        .
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">
          Incorrecto.
          <m:math>
            <m:mrow>
              <m:msup>
                <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                <m:mn>0</m:mn>
              </m:msup>
              <m:mo>≠</m:mo>
              <m:mn>6</m:mn>
              <m:mo>·</m:mo>
              <m:mn>0</m:mn>
            </m:mrow>
          </m:math>
          . En efecto,
          <m:math>
            <m:mrow>
              <m:mn>6</m:mn>
              <m:mo>·</m:mo>
              <m:mn>0</m:mn>
              <m:mo>=</m:mo>
              <m:mn>0</m:mn>
            </m:mrow>
          </m:math>
          , pero una potencia con base distinta de
          <m:math>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn>
          </m:math>
          y exponente
          <m:math>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn>
          </m:math>
          vale
          <m:math>
            <m:mn>1</m:mn>
          </m:math>
          ; por eso
          <m:math>
            <m:mrow>
              <m:msup>
                <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                <m:mn>0</m:mn>
              </m:msup>
              <m:mo>=</m:mo>
              <m:mn>1</m:mn>
            </m:mrow>
          </m:math>
          .
        </qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        Porque toda potencia con base distinta de
        <m:math>
          <m:mn>0</m:mn>
        </m:math>
        y exponente
        <m:math>
          <m:mn>0</m:mn>
        </m:math>
        es igual a
        <m:math>
          <m:mn>1</m:mn>
        </m:math>
        .
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">
          ¡Correcto! La base es
          <m:math>
            <m:mn>6</m:mn>
          </m:math>
          , que es distinta de
          <m:math>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn>
          </m:math>
          , y el exponente es
          <m:math>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn>
          </m:math>
          . Por la regla de las potencias, toda potencia con base distinta de
          <m:math>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn>
          </m:math>
          y exponente
          <m:math>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn>
          </m:math>
          es igual a
          <m:math>
            <m:mn>1</m:mn>
          </m:math>
          ; por eso
          <m:math>
            <m:mrow>
              <m:msup>
                <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                <m:mn>0</m:mn>
              </m:msup>
              <m:mo>=</m:mo>
              <m:mn>1</m:mn>
            </m:mrow>
          </m:math>
          .
        </qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        Porque si el exponente es
        <m:math>
          <m:mn>0</m:mn>
        </m:math>
        , el resultado siempre es
        <m:math>
          <m:mn>0</m:mn>
        </m:math>
        .
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">
          Incorrecto. La afirmación “si el exponente es
          <m:math>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn>
          </m:math>
          , el resultado siempre es
          <m:math>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn>
          </m:math>
          ” es falsa. Un contraejemplo concreto es
          <m:math>
            <m:mrow>
              <m:msup>
                <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                <m:mn>0</m:mn>
              </m:msup>
              <m:mo>=</m:mo>
              <m:mn>1</m:mn>
            </m:mrow>
          </m:math>
          , no
          <m:math>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn>
          </m:math>
          . En este ejercicio también ocurre que
          <m:math>
            <m:mrow>
              <m:msup>
                <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                <m:mn>0</m:mn>
              </m:msup>
              <m:mo>=</m:mo>
              <m:mn>1</m:mn>
            </m:mrow>
          </m:math>
          .
        </qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        Porque
        <m:math>
          <m:msup>
            <m:mn>6</m:mn>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn>
          </m:msup>
        </m:math>
        significa sumar seis veces el número
        <m:math>
          <m:mn>0</m:mn>
        </m:math>
        .
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">
          Incorrecto. Sumar seis veces el número
          <m:math>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn>
          </m:math>
          da
          <m:math>
            <m:mrow>
              <m:mn>0</m:mn>
              <m:mo>+</m:mo>
              <m:mn>0</m:mn>
              <m:mo>+</m:mo>
              <m:mn>0</m:mn>
              <m:mo>+</m:mo>
              <m:mn>0</m:mn>
              <m:mo>+</m:mo>
              <m:mn>0</m:mn>
              <m:mo>+</m:mo>
              <m:mn>0</m:mn>
              <m:mo>=</m:mo>
              <m:mn>0</m:mn>
            </m:mrow>
          </m:math>
          , pero en este caso
          <m:math>
            <m:mrow>
              <m:msup>
                <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                <m:mn>0</m:mn>
              </m:msup>
              <m:mo>=</m:mo>
              <m:mn>1</m:mn>
            </m:mrow>
          </m:math>
          porque toda potencia con base distinta de
          <m:math>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn>
          </m:math>
          y exponente
          <m:math>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn>
          </m:math>
          es igual a
          <m:math>
            <m:mn>1</m:mn>
          </m:math>
          .
        </qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Evaluar la potencia </strong>
              <m:math>
                <m:msup>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                </m:msup>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:msup>
                    <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                  </m:msup>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>×</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>×</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>×</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>16</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Entonces, el paso (1) está correcto.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Justificar por qué </strong>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:msup>
                    <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>0</m:mn>
                  </m:msup>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Se aplica la regla de las potencias: toda potencia con base distinta de <m:math><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:math> y exponente <m:math><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:math> es igual a <m:math><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>≠</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>0</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:msup>
                    <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>0</m:mn>
                  </m:msup>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Por eso, la explicación correcta es la alternativa B.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Reemplazar en la expresión original</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:msup>
                    <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>0</m:mn>
                  </m:msup>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:msup>
                    <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                  </m:msup>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>16</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Sumar</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>16</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>17</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El paso (2) se justifica porque toda potencia con base distinta de <m:math><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:math> y exponente <m:math><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:math> es igual a <m:math><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:math>. La respuesta correcta es la alternativa B.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>